title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-02-2013 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-02-2013 MON












The Glenn Beck Program - 09/02/13 






Joe Pags fills in for Glenn Beck.

 Joe shares his perspective on the Obama administration's approach to dealing with Syria
 and the rest of the Middle East.

 Lt. Col. Jeffrey Addicott, director of the Center for Terrorism Law at St. Mary's University,
 weighs in on the Syria situation.

 Joe then discusses the assault on both Christianity and the civil liberties of business owners.

 TheBlaze editor-at-large Mike Opelka covers TheBlaze headlines of the holiday weekend.




The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET
